## Feature Workflow — Ticket > Wireframe > Approve > Build > Test

**Every new feature follows this sequence. No step may be skipped.**

1. **Ticket First** — create in task tracker with title, description, and DoD before any implementation
2. **Wireframe / Design First** — for UI features: update the design file before writing any code. STOP and ask for review.
3. **Human Approves** — explicit approval required. Silence is not consent.
4. **Implement** — build exactly what was approved
5. **Test** — add smoke test assertions, run all tests, verify in browser

**Exempt:** bug fixes, copy tweaks, and non-visual backend changes (no wireframe needed, but still need a ticket).
